{
  "name": "react-native-ota-sdk",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "React Native SDK for seamless Over-The-Air (OTA) updates. Supports major APK updates and minor JavaScript bundle updates with WiFi force-update capabilities. Optional Firebase backend: upload APK to Storage → Cloud Function updates Remote Config → app fetches config. No server needed. Compatible with React Native old and new architecture (TurboModules).",
